name: Gunslingers of the Runic Shroom
description: There are Rootmason carvings all over the heirlooms of the Gunslingers of the Runic Shroom. Why? How? They also have a heavy amount of Primordyceps in their diet. Recently they’ve been feeling a little… different. Now operating as members of the Skywinder Cult, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
